name: LUCK FOR NUCKS TEE
description: The PLAYOFFS ARE HERE! We decided to make something special for our team's 2012 cup run, maybe give them a little extra luck this year to get through that final series! And here it is, our very own Lucky Cat, complete in Vancouver colours and foam finger... ready to cheer our team on! Be sure to pick one up quick as we only made a limited number of them! Get one now and represent your home team! *Also available in Womens' sizing! This tee features a 5-color print on a 100% cotton Royal Blue t-shirt with woven sizing and hem labels. 100% Made in North America.

name: LUCK FOR NUCKS STICKERS
description:
The PLAYOFFS ARE HERE!

To go along with our Limited Edition 'Luck for Nucks' T-shirt, we created these awesome stickers with the same design!  Measuring 4.5" x 3", you'll be able to show your support wherever you go!  

Shipping is free for these stickers, no matter how many your order.. so get as many as you'd like and show some love for the home team on their playoff run!

name: TANUKI (SILVER)
description: Tanuki is known in Japanese folklore as mischievous and jolly, a master of disguise and shapeshifting, but somewhat gullible and absentminded. At Origami Ghost, our Tanuki is much the same, but also likes to dabble in some street art.. tonight he's ready for some wheat pasting in the downtown eastside. This tee features a 3-color print on a 100% cotton silver t-shirt with woven sizing and hem labels. 100% Made in North America.

name: FOLD TEE
description: What symbolizes Origami more than the action of 'Folding'? We created this simple, clean graphic to boldly state the word. This tee features a 3-color print on a 100% cotton t-shirt with woven sizing and hem labels. 100% Made in North America.

name: OG RAGLAN (BLACK)
description: Baseball season is just getting underway, so for our Spring 2012 collection we decided to make a clean and simple looking 3/4 Sleeve Baseball Raglan. Featuring a folded 'OG' monogram, this is a perfect shirt to wear to the diamond. This tee features a 2-color print on a 50/50 3/4 Sleeve Baseball Raglan with woven sizing and and a special 'Neatly Folded' Hem label. 100% Made in North America.

name: LOGO HOODIE (BLACK)
description: It's back to basics - where it all began with the Origami Ghost Logo Hoodie. This black hoodie features the Origami Ghost logo printed on a 100% cotton hooded sweatshirt. *This hoodie is UNISEX sizing, so it runs pretty snug. We recommend that you order a size up from your regular Men's t-shirt size. (Girls, you should order a your normal t-shirt size. If you wear a girl's small t-shirt, order a unisex small hoodie) 100% Made in North America.

name: ORANGE GUMMI CAT (MENS)
description: What did the 11 year-old versions of ourselves do whenever we got some cash-ola for Christmas? Spend it on candy of course! So for Boxing Day 2011 - we took care of our inner-child needs & created this Gummi Bear parody with none other than our own Maneki Neko (Lucky Cat)! Ricky started eating the red one already since it's his favourite colour, so don't mind the bite out of its head! And the same goes with Colin and the green one, but don't worry - the Orange one is completely intact if you rather have one to yourself. The tee has a 4-color design printed on the front and a 4-color design printed on the back of a 100% cotton white tshirt; it also features custom woven sizing and hem labels. This is the page for Men's sizes, for women's sizing please CLICK HERE 100% Made in North America.

name: FOLD ALONE (MENS)
description: 'HOME ALONE' or in our case, 'FOLD ALONE' is here in time for the holiday season. Based on one of our favourite Christmas movies, the Origami Ghost Lucky Cat plans an impostor Kevin McCalister. No Kevin impersonator is complete without his favourite cheese pizza from Little Nero's Pizza. 'FOLD ALONE' is an Origami Ghost Special Edition Tee, limited to only 50 prints. The tee has a 5-color design printed on the front and a 3-color design printed on the back of a 100% cotton navy tshirt; it also features custom woven sizing and hem labels. name: DOMO ARIGATO (MENS)
description: Thank you Mr. Roboto! We've hooked up with Calgary-based artist Davey Gravy (and his grand mother) for a cross-stitch inspired t-shirt based on the classic song, "Mister Roboto." We can't guarantee the song won't get stuck in your head. 'DOMO ARIGATO' has a 5-color design printed on the front and a 3-color design printed on the back of a 100% cotton white tshirt; it also features custom woven sizing and hem labels. This is the page for men's sizes, for women's sizing please CLICK HERE 100% Made in North America.

name: MANEKI NEKO (MENS)
description: It's Lucky Cat 2.0! If you're trying to score some luck and you don't want to be carrying around a live cat or a porcelain figurine, then this shirt is for you! With our latest reincarnation of the Lucky Cat - you'll find it's back to the basics with Maneki Neko in his traditional form! 'MANEKI NEKO' is a 5-color design printed on a 100% cotton black tshirt, and features custom woven sizing and hem labels. This is the page for Men's sizes, for women's sizing please CLICK HERE 100% Made in North America.
